2008-01-18 W. Martin Borgert <debacle@debian.org>

	* Version 0.4.8 now under GPL-3.

2003-01-26 W. Borgert <debacle@debian.org>

	* Version 0.4.6 released.

	* blinkd.c: Hopefully better handling of keyboard device.

	* configure.ac: Added AM_MAINTAINER_MODE to get finally rid of
	  autoconf and automake dependencies.

	* Added web page stuff for savannah (http://www.nongnu.org/blinkd/).

2002-11-19 W. Borgert <debacle@debian.org>

	* Version 0.4.5 released.

	* Using new autoconf/automake.

	* Manual pages now based on DocBook/XML instead of DocBook/SGML.

2002-07-28 W. Borgert <debacle@debian.org>

	* Version 0.4.3 released.

	* debian/control: Added a conflict with ledcontrol.

2001-10-24 W. Borgert <debacle@debian.org>

	* Version 0.4.2 released.

	* Using new autoconf/automake.

	* No user visible changes.

2001-02-04 W. Borgert <debacle@debian.org>

	* Version 0.4 released.

	* Options for blinkd are now set in /etc/default/blinkd.

2000-05-01  W. Borgert <debacle@debian.org>

	* Version 0.3.6 released.

	* Added option --no-reopen to blinkd.  Forbids blinkd to
	  close/reopen /dev/console to prevent from disk access.

1999-10-19  W. Borgert <debacle@debian.org>

	* Changed man pages.

	* Version 0.3.1 released.

1999-10-19  W. Borgert <debacle@debian.org>

	* Changed man pages.

	* Version 0.3.1 released.

1999-06-29  W. Borgert <debacle@debian.org>

	* Version 0.3.0 released.

	* Using gettext for i18n.

	* Using pthreads internally.

	* Using docbook (SGML) for man page.

	* Supporting all three PC keyboard LEDs.

1999-02-14  W. Borgert  <debacle@debian.org>

	* Version 0.2.1 released.

	* Added some files in doc directory.

1999-02-13  W. Borgert  <debacle@debian.org>

	* Version 0.2 released.

	* configure.in etc.: Using autoconf/automake now.

	* blink.c/blinkd.c: Preliminary changes for gettext.

	* blink.c: New option for using remote server.

	* blink.c: Allow '+' and '-' for incrementing/decrementing blink
	  rate.
